" He is steady and firm, and that's where we should be because we're abiding in Him.

00:47:42.872 --> 00:47:44.783
I am not moved by what I see or feel; I am moved by what the Word says.

00:47:44.783 --> 00:47:50.360
He's moved by faith in what the Word says.

00:47:50.360 --> 00:47:57.696
As you stand in faith and believe Him, He will meet your needs.

00:47:57.696 --> 00:48:01.612
He's not moved by the emotion of crying and bellowing.

00:48:01.612 --> 00:48:07.640
Take the emotion out of it and go to Him boldly.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
"Father, You said in Your word You would do this.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
" That's how Jesus resisted the devil.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
He spoke to him; he said, "It is written, devil.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
" He wasn't moved.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Stand steadfast like a solid pillar.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
My house is built upon the Rock.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
When the storms of life come, they don't knock down my house.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
My house is built on a firm foundation.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.300
The name of the Lord is a strong tower, and the righteous run to it and are safe.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
That's what we stand on today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
No matter the drama in the news, we're not moved by it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
We take our authority over the nations, our area, our house, and our town.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
We pray over our government and leadership.

